 One of the companies that we're working with is in the travel space, which is about a $2 trillion market.

2
00:00:05,040 --> 00:00:12,160
 Now, that's an opportunity to understand what you're going to build this company into, and you can start to build the roadmap to get there.

3
00:00:12,160 --> 00:00:24,000
 Clientele and customers that want to continually recommend your service or your product to other people, you're reducing your customer acquisition costs dramatically.

4
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:27,800
 What do you actually want to do with this company? Because a lot of founders, they're in build mode.

5
00:00:27,800 --> 00:00:32,080
 They haven't had the chance to think, what do I actually want to build this into?

6
00:00:32,080 --> 00:00:39,560
 Do I want to exit with $5 million, go do it again? Do I want to exit with $20 million, be able to go retire, chill on a beach in Montenegro?

7
