 Brandon, in one of the articles I read about you is that you went from moving loans at 11 years old to helping startup raise the insane numbers that we mentioned.

19
00:01:56,820 --> 00:02:02,440
 Can you briefly walk us through that journey and introduce yourself a bit more to the audience?

20
