 Definitely. Yeah. So, very uncommon. I get this question a lot.

21
00:02:06,860 --> 00:02:11,300
 How did you end up in VC? And I don't have a traditional answer.

22
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:16,520
 I went into finance and then I got into VC or I went into big consulting and got into VC.

23
